<qa bind:longpress="addHandle" wx:if="{{item}}" mini="{{false}}" answer="{{true}}" class="container qa" item="{{item}}"></qa>
<box padding="30"  wx:if="{{!item.answer && !answerPeermission}}" >
  <view class="waiting empty" style="margin-bottom:20rpx;">
    <image src="/assets/images/waiting.png" style="margin-bottom:20rpx;" ></image>
    该问题还未收到回复
    <button bindtap="addHandle" style="margin-top:20rpx;" class="btn primary plain">我来回答</button>
  </view>
</box>

<mycard hat wx:if="{{ answerPeermission }}" title="编辑回答">
    <textarea  class="answer-input" placeholder='输入你的答案' value="{{item.answer}}" bindinput="answerInput"></textarea>
    <button class="answer-submit" bindtap="submitHandle"  class="btn primary">提交回答</button>

</mycard>



<recoms count="5" group="rental"></recoms>
